Package genefinder

Class ProcessFastq

java.lang.Object
genefinder.ProcessFastq
public class ProcessFastq
extends java.lang.Object
This is a class to import Fastq files into String, and process it. This finds all genes based on start and stop codon, calculate length of gene, GC ratio and find specific sequences in genes.
Author:
hyunyongjin
